Human beings are autonomous entities capable of realizing the potentialities generated by social evolution throughout their lives, based on conscious decisions. Freedom can be understood in both a negative sense, referring to the ability to make choices and establish relationships, and a positive sense, which encompasses mastery over natural forces and the development of human creativity.
